{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act46side", "eventName": "雪山降臨1101", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "OS-4", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "並蒂生", "storyInfo": "菈塔托絲與維多利亞大使第二次會面，暗示要解決阿克托斯這個麻煩。茱安娜與恩雅關係開始破冰，又再次遭遇刺客的襲擊。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g8_nobleroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "kc"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煩死了！不是和你們說過今天別再打擾我了嗎？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是誰在——", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……姐姐。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼來了……", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快坐下，怎麼了？睡不著嗎？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尤卡坦怎麼搞的，明明叫他盯好你——", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她搖了搖頭。"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，是我不讓尤卡坦跟來的。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想單獨和你談談。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "菈塔托絲從未想過，會在這個直率開朗的妹妹臉上看到這樣的神色。"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，不過只能一下下，然後就乖乖去睡覺。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是的……都是當媽媽的人了，怎麼還像個小孩一樣。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我今天，聽到了阿克托斯在客廳裡大吼大叫……", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "菈塔托絲", "content": "還是吵到你了？"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "菈塔托絲", "content": "該死的，回頭必須找他算帳……"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……不是……", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽到了你們爭論的事，我也知道這段時間，謝拉格發生了很多糟糕的事……", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "菈塔……我請求你。如果你知道些什麼，一定、一定要告訴我。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶拉岡德在上……", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "休露絲，這些都不是你現在應該操心的事。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心吧，等你接手了這一大攤子的事之後，多的是讓你操心的機會。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，最近的變故一件接著一件，就算我一直待在房間裡，也能感覺到一切都在變得很糟……", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每天都能在窗戶外面看見愁眉不展的人，還有莫希她，到現在還是一點消息都沒有……", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還在派人尋找她的下落……我相信她不會有事的，別忘了，她現在可是布朗陶家最厲害的戰士之一。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我當然知道……", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我更擔心的是你，菈塔。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然以前我也不太能幫上你的什麼忙，但至少還能站在你身邊，給你一點支持……", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是現在，只有你一個人應付這一切……菈塔，我還是希望你能多和我說說話。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不用一個人堅持什麼，我和尤卡坦，在任何時候都一定會支持你的。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你想的太多了，我的傻瓜妹妹。你是在懷疑我當不好這個家主，想要早點接班了？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不是——", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我向你發誓，休露絲。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會保護好你，還有尤卡坦，以及整個布朗陶家。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算豁出性命，我也一定會做到。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶拉岡德見證，絕不食言。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了？你就算不信我，還能不信耶拉岡德嗎？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒必要把話說得那麼重……", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好……那你答應我，現在就去休息。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心吧，明天一定會比今天更好……", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "45_g7_lakescenery_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很榮幸收到您的邀請，尊敬的布朗陶夫人。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您在這個時候主動約見我，想必是改變主意了？", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……少說廢話。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "刺殺希瓦艾什家和佩爾羅契家的人、離間三族關係，這就是你們逼迫我與你們合作的方式？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，我原本以為維多利亞的政治家至少會用更聰明一點的手段。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "男人不置可否地笑了笑。"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "布朗陶夫人，我不明白您為何會這樣想。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在別國境內刺殺該國的領導人，這可是毫無疑問的宣戰行為……如果被證實的話。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您確定要對維多利亞提出這樣的指控嗎？", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這就是你們有恃無恐的理由。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尊敬的夫人，恐怕我還是不明白您的意思。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過既然您今天選擇與我見面，那我十分樂意聽您講講——有什麼是我可以為您效勞的？", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……哼，得意吧，你們粗糙的計謀還是達成了目的，起碼佩爾羅契和布朗陶的關係已經徹底破裂，在其他人眼裡我也戴上了可疑的帽子。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於恩希歐迪斯……那套什麼三家都想要穩定的話術，就是臨時編出來騙騙阿克托斯那個傻子的。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他心裡清楚得很，以謝拉格的現狀，一旦某家領袖“意外”遇害，只要有人稍微挑撥，失去最後希望的本地領民們肯定會一哄而散。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬一我們見面的事被他知道了，就算他清楚我沒有答應你們任何事情，也會毫不猶豫帶著佩爾羅契向我發難。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟現在的謝拉格，急缺一位能擔負所有的“罪人”。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以他的手腕，最壞的下場，就是布朗陶家從此斷絕於謝拉格。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我的時間不多了。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很同情您的處境，夫人。我也認為您對局勢的分析一點不差。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，您是否有意打破這樣的局面呢？", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那我們就別廢話了。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "首先，我要你們絕對的承諾——不管在任何情況下，都要優先保證布朗陶家的安全，還有領民的安全。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，我們素來同情被希瓦艾什邊緣化的普通本地民眾，這是我們推進與謝拉格和平合作的初心之一。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖……隨你怎麼說。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其次，將來布朗陶家接替喀蘭貿易與維多利亞合作的時候，目前的一切貿易政策不得改變，維多利亞也不得收回對謝拉格的援助。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "否則，我們隨時會中斷與維多利亞的合作——這也不會是你們想要的局面。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夫人，您實在是多慮了。與謝拉格的和平合作我們求之不得，又怎麼會主動破壞？", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當您成為謝拉格唯一的代言人之後，我們還有很多可以合作的空間。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好……", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過想要取代喀蘭貿易不是一朝一夕能夠完成的，我們都需要時間準備……當務之急，就是先擺平阿克托斯。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以我對那個阿克托斯的瞭解，只要讓他發現布朗陶和維多利亞合作，他一定會想辦法再找我麻煩。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "菈塔托絲", "content": "某種程度上他比恩希歐迪斯更加棘手……"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "菈塔托絲", "content": "這個蠢貨！"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是十分遺憾……", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#7$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請布朗陶夫人決定吧。對於阿克托斯，我們該如何爭取一下呢？", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#7$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會再找阿克托斯，最後好好地“談一次”。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……哦？", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#7$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在領地西南的山腳下，布朗陶家還留有一個祖宅，附近幾乎無人居住。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會傳消息給阿克托斯，以說明真相為由，約他明天到那裡談話。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "時間就定在晚上七點，也就是十五個小時後。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望……維多利亞能夠證明自己的誠意。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，不會讓您失望的，夫人。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們也衷心地希望，您能夠“說服”佩爾羅契家族。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "40_g2_glacier", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#5$2", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "200,0"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$wasteland_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormflp", "volume": 0.8, "loop": "true", "channel": "wind"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_reedmarshes", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "r"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.8, "channel": "r", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_lightsnow", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "stopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "r", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "山風夾雜雪沫，觸響著屋簷的乾草。"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾片脆弱的枯葉被風捲起，飄往坐在屋頂的少女的髮辮上，她捻下這些雜物，雙指輕輕揉搓。"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#5$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "裂雲獸從少女的肩後探出腦袋，碰了碰她通紅的臉頰。"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，裂雲獸……", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#5$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只想……坐在這裡散散心，你不用陪我一起吹冷風。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "白色的小生靈發出“咕嚕咕嚕”的聲音，牠已經和茱安娜一起度過了無數難熬的日夜。"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你……", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……不知道該怎麼面對聖女……大人……", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她是耶拉岡德的代行者，按理說我應該敬愛她，但是——", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼會發生那種事，為什麼還要懲罰我們家……", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少女將裂雲獸擁入懷中，靜靜在屋頂上坐著，直到細密的雪花將她的頭髮染上一層銀白。"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "stopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "wind", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "67_G5_statueworkshop", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_lightsnow", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通往木屋後院的門被推開了。"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來訪者為後院的雪地新添了幾處淺淺的腳印。恩雅走向左側，她看見三把擺放凌亂的弩，拾起一把端詳起來。"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "似乎要比茱安娜使用的弩小上一圈。"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅向前望去，不遠處立著三個箭靶，還留著幾支沒有回收的弩箭。"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#2$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼小的年紀就要開始訓練了嗎……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#2$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把手上還刻著名字……是她弟弟妹妹的嗎？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#2$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "院子另一頭堆放的雜物此時吸引了恩雅的目光。那邊空地上橫七豎八地倒了一地雕像，但她仍一眼看見了雕像上令人懷念的面容。"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅走向其中最大的雕像，將它握舉在身前。雕刻它的工匠，技術顯然已經爐火純青——耶拉岡德正對著恩雅，露出祂溫和的微笑。"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "恩雅", "content": "這不是……"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "恩雅", "content": "和我們在銀心湖敲定的雕像差不多嘛。"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來你在大家心底都是這個樣子呢。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而腳邊還有略顯不同的作品，恩雅又拿起一個。"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新拿起的雕像纖細了一些，五官也稍顯粗糙，甚至讓人覺得面目刻薄。多半是工匠在雕刻臉部時沒掌握好力度，削得過頭了。"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "45_g9_underkjerastastue", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_250_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_250_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "果然還是不太適合吧，和耶拉岡德根本不像！", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#4$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少臉要再瘦一點，身材也……", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#4$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_250_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女大人，也請聽聽您侍女小小的願望吧。", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#7$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_250_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅，最好的恩雅~", "name": "雅兒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_250_1#3$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "67_G5_statueworkshop", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_lightsnow", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在知道了吧？臉寬一點更好看。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一大一小的兩個雕像，被鄭重地擺放了回去。"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在荒涼而陌生的院子裡，恩雅雙手合十，如蔓珠院長老們那般，虔敬地面朝耶拉岡德的雕像。"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她沒有許下任何具體的願望，她只是期待一個奇蹟降臨。"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "67_G10_kjeragwilde_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太陽已經下山，小獵手依然獨自坐在院中。"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看到恩雅，女孩連忙準備起身行禮，恩雅卻緊緊按住了她的手臂。"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……聖女大人。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用這樣，反正又沒有別人，我們就省略這些繁文縟節吧。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另外，我還是希望你能叫我恩雅。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……聽您吩咐。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "打完招呼，女孩又把頭轉到一邊，不再言語。"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了……我看到院子裡有很多耶拉岡德的雕像，都是你們自己製作的嗎？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（沉默地點頭）", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，形象好像也不太一樣，是因為大家對古籍中記載的耶拉岡德形象有不同的理解？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "像的那些是爸爸雕的，不像的是我雕的……", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噗嗤——", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起……！不過我想問問，你們為什麼要做這麼多耶拉岡德的雕像？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……在很久以前，我們家從佩爾羅契家分出來，按照耶拉岡德的指引進入雪山，從此世世代代都是獵人。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們相信，山上的生命一同分有了耶拉岡德的靈魂，我們作為祂的一部分在此循環往復，生生不息。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因感念耶拉岡德的恩賜，每個家族成員從能夠獨自狩獵開始，都需要學習製作耶拉岡德像。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以及其他帶有祂印記的皮衣、骨雕和擺飾等等。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“獵人有福，且聽一言。”", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“風行草偃，豈非祂之偈語？飛禽走獸，豈非祂之化物？”", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“生滅循環，猶是冰水變換；未有始者，亦不有終。”", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“獨講與你，耶拉岡德之智與愛。”", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“不倚異兆，唯尋雪山”……然後，然後是——", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#4$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“方能與祂共契。”", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就是這段……它和《耶拉岡德》其他很多部分都不一樣，我總是背一句忘一句。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#4$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "經書裡的細枝末節沒有那麼重要。只需常常提醒自己，耶拉岡德在傾聽和凝視著我們的言行。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然這些拗口的詞句背不通順，但你在盡力生活。狩獵、雕刻，這一舉一動都在恪守祂的教誨。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使是聖女……如果我沒有遇到茱安娜，或許終其一生都無法真正通曉這一段落的要義。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#9$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是我所見過最虔誠的信徒之一，我知道，耶拉岡德會保佑你們一家幸福的。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#9$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#5$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的是這樣嗎？", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#5$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，畢竟我是祂……選中的聖女。我相信，無論多麼艱難，祂都會顯現在我們最需要的時刻。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚——", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一向以堅強示人的小獵人，稚嫩的臉龐上淌下兩行淚珠，掉落在她和恩雅的腳邊。"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "茱安娜？發生什麼事了？能和我說說嗎？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#6$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我——", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅緊緊握住茱安娜失控顫抖的雙手。"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛學會打獵的時候，被一頭源石感染的野獸咬傷……得了礦石病……", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了幫我治病……父親他天天打完獵，回家還要趕工做那些雕像，拿去城裡換點藥……就這麼年復一年……", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前幾天，父親的朋友告訴我……天災的那天，父親他……就在車站……", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果不是我——", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚……嗚啊……", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "茱安娜……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶拉岡德，為什麼……", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothtrailground", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g21_skystarry_L2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哀慟的少女坐倒在地，抱著膝蓋蜷縮起來。"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅蹲伏在一旁，竭力構思著慰藉的言詞，但她的思緒掠盡經書也沒有找出一句，伸出的手遲疑了一下，輕撫少女的後背。"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的喉嚨哽咽滯悶。如果永恆的耶拉岡德也會斂聲息語，那祂的聖女又能做到什麼呢？"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雅兒，你在聽嗎……"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "67_G10_kjeragwilde_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“咕嚕咕嚕”，窗邊的裂雲獸像是看見什麼，用牠能發出的最大的動靜喊叫著，一溜煙又跑回了茱安娜的帽兜裡。"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "茱安娜吸了吸鼻子，用掌根匆匆擦去兩頰的淚水。"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……院子外面有人來了，我去開門。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好心的小姐……", "name": "路過的老人"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請問……最近的小鎮該怎麼走？", "name": "路過的老人"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是迷路了嗎……您能從這裡看見那邊的燈光嗎？您只要沿著這條路往山下走，遇到岔路口就朝著有燈的地方——", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉……天這麼黑，我的眼睛看不到……", "name": "路過的老人"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "茱安娜", "content": "我來送——"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "茱安娜", "content": "不行……我還不能離開。"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老爺爺，要不您在這裡留住一晚，等天亮了再下山吧。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，算了，不麻煩你了。我還是自己慢慢走下山吧……", "name": "路過的老人"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crutch_snow", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "false", "channel": "nw"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.5, "channel": "nw"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事，就是一個迷路的老爺爺。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 427, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你住在這麼遠離城鎮的地方，平時經常有人路過嗎？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有我們一家住在這裡，基本沒見過什麼路人，聖女大人您還是第一個……", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "StopMusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——小心！", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#8$1"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_arrowshot", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_arrow", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "false", "channel": "s1", "delay": 0.3}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bowstring", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "false", "channel": "s2", "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bowstring_rebound", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "false", "channel": "s3", "delay": 0.6}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "xstrength": 25.0, "ystrength": 25.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "stopmusic